5A202CB1.Line1.6DE47: We follow her into Hatred itself. It will sour our hearts even more, turn us against each other.

8E091FB5.Line5.6DE47: Whether we use you or the stone, we have to stop her.

F414A633.Line3.6DE47: Let’s remember why we’re here. Together.

FB3FFC35.MenuLabel: “Lilith. She hungers for her father’s power.”
